<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <style>
        .privacy-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: white;
        }
        .privacy-header {
            background: #73B14B;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: -40px -20px 40px -20px;
        }
        .privacy-header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .privacy-header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .privacy-content h2 {
            color: #2A5220;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .privacy-content h3 {
            color: #2A5220;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .privacy-content p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .privacy-content ul {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }
        .privacy-content li {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #73B14B;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            background: #2A5220;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .effective-date {
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #73B14B;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .contact-box strong {
            color: #2A5220;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="privacy-container">
        <div class="privacy-header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>Better Southgate Leisure Centre</p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-content">
            <p class="effective-date">Last updated: November 2025</p>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Better Southgate Leisure Centre ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you submit feedback through our customer feedback system.</p>

            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>When you submit feedback through our system, we may collect the following information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Activity Information:</strong> The activity you participated in (required)</li>
                <li><strong>Rating:</strong> Your satisfaction rating (required)</li>
                <li><strong>Comments:</strong> Your written feedback (required)</li>
                <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> Your email (optional)</li>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> Your name (optional)</li>
                <li><strong>Better Membership ID:</strong> Your membership number (optional)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Improve our facilities and services</li>
                <li>Understand customer satisfaction levels</li>
                <li>Identify areas for improvement</li>
                <li>Respond to your feedback if you've provided contact details</li>
                <li>Analyze trends in customer experience</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
            <p>We process your personal data on the basis of:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Consent:</strong> You provide explicit consent when submitting feedback</li>
                <li><strong>Legitimate Interest:</strong> Improving our services and facilities for all customers</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>5. Who Has Access to Your Information</h2>
            <p>Your feedback is only accessible to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Authorized Better Southgate Leisure Centre staff members</li>
                <li>Staff members use secure login credentials to access the feedback portal</li>
                <li>We do not share your information with third parties</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your feedback for <strong>one year</strong> from the date of submission. After this period, your feedback is automatically deleted from our system.</p>

            <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Encrypted data transmission (HTTPS)</li>
                <li>Secure password-protected staff access</li>
                <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
                <li>Cloud-based secure database storage</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>8. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
            <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> Request a copy of the feedback you submitted</li>
                <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
                <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your feedback before the automatic 1-year deletion</li>
                <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong> Request limitation on how we use your data</li>
                <li><strong>Right to Data Portability:</strong> Request your data in a portable format</li>
                <li><strong>Right to Object:</strong> Object to processing of your personal data</li>
                <li><strong>Right to Withdraw Consent:</strong> Withdraw consent at any time</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>9. Optional Information</h2>
            <p>All personal information fields (name, email, membership ID) are <strong>completely optional</strong>. You can submit anonymous feedback by leaving these fields blank. We encourage you to only provide information you're comfortable sharing.</p>

            <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Our feedback system is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

            <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when the policy was last revised. Continued use of our feedback system after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

            <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
            <div class="contact-box">
                <p><strong>To exercise your data rights or if you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:</strong></p>
                <p>
                    Better Southgate Leisure Centre<br>
                    Winchmore Hill Road<br>
                    London N14 6AD<br>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Email: <a href="mailto:southgate@gll.org" style="color: #73B14B;">southgate@gll.org</a><br>
                    Phone: 020 8886 8090
                </p>
            </div>

            <h2>13. Data Controller</h2>
            <p>The data controller responsible for your personal data is:</p>
            <p>
                <strong>GLL (Greenwich Leisure Limited)</strong><br>
                Middlegate House, The Royal Arsenal<br>
                London SE18 6SX<br>
                Company Registration Number: 1812398
            </p>

            <h2>14. Supervisory Authority</h2>
            <p>If you have concerns about how we handle your data, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO):</p>
            <p>
                Website: <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" style="color: #73B14B;">ico.org.uk</a><br>
                Phone: 0303 123 1113
            </p>

            <a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to Feedback Form</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>